      "risk": "Weather API latency or downtime affects feature freshness",
      "severity": "low",
      "mitigation": "Weather features are precomputed hourly, not fetched at request time. Stale weather data (up to 2 hours old) has minimal impact on delivery time prediction. Feature Pipeline retries with exponential backoff."
